---
// src/pages/legal/privacy-policy.astro
import LegalLayout from '../../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for AI Tools Idea — how we collect, use, and protect your data."
  lastUpdated="May 18, 2025"
>

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>AI Tools Idea ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website <strong>aitoolsidea.com</strong> (the "Site"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our Site.</p>
  <p>Please read this policy carefully. If you disagree with its terms, please discontinue use of the Site.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

  <h3>Information you provide directly</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Email address</strong> — when you subscribe to our newsletter or contact us</li>
    <li><strong>Name</strong> — optionally provided when subscribing</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
  <p>When you visit the Site, we automatically collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Usage data</strong>: pages visited, time spent, referring URLs, browser type, operating system</li>
    <li><strong>IP address</strong>: used for analytics and security purposes (anonymised where possible)</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies</strong>: see Section 6 below</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Information from third parties</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Analytics providers</strong> (Google Analytics): aggregate traffic data</li>
    <li><strong>Advertising networks</strong>: if you click affiliate links, those third parties may collect data per their own privacy policies</li>
  </ul>

  <hr />

  <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use collected information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Operate, maintain, and improve the Site</li>
    <li>Send you our email newsletter (only if you subscribed)</li>
    <li>Respond to your enquiries and support requests</li>
    <li>Monitor and analyse usage patterns to improve user experience</li>
    <li>Detect and prevent fraudulent or abusive activity</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal data to third parties.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
  <p>If you are in the European Economic Area (EEA), we process your data under the following legal bases:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Consent</strong>: for newsletter subscriptions and non-essential cookies</li>
    <li><strong>Legitimate interests</strong>: for site analytics and security</li>
    <li><strong>Legal obligation</strong>: where required by applicable law</li>
  </ul>

  <hr />

  <h2>5. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
  <p>We may share your information with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Service providers</strong>: email platforms (Brevo/Sendinblue), analytics tools, hosting providers — only as necessary to operate the Site and under strict data processing agreements</li>
    <li><strong>Legal authorities</strong>: if required by law, court order, or governmental authority</li>
    <li><strong>Business transfers</strong>: in the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do not share your personal data with advertisers or data brokers.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use cookies to:</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Cookie type</th>
        <th>Purpose</th>
        <th>Duration</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Essential</td>
        <td>Site functionality, security</td>
        <td>Session</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Analytics</td>
        <td>Google Analytics (anonymised)</td>
        <td>2 years</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Preferences</td>
        <td>Remember your settings</td>
        <td>1 year</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Opting out of analytics cookies will not affect your ability to use the Site.</p>
  <p>For full details, see our <a href="/legal/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>7. Affiliate Links</h2>
  <p>This Site participates in affiliate programmes. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission. Affiliate partners may set their own cookies and collect data subject to their own privacy policies. We have no control over third-party data practices.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We retain your data for as long as necessary to provide our services:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Newsletter subscribers</strong>: until you unsubscribe</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics data</strong>: 26 months (Google Analytics default)</li>
    <li><strong>Contact enquiries</strong>: 12 months</li>
  </ul>

  <hr />

  <h2>9. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Access</strong> the personal data we hold about you</li>
    <li><strong>Correct</strong> inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
    <li><strong>Delete</strong> your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
    <li><strong>Restrict</strong> or <strong>object to</strong> our processing of your data</li>
    <li><strong>Data portability</strong>: receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
    <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> at any time (where processing is based on consent)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise any of these rights, email us at: <strong>privacy@aitoolsidea.com</strong></p>

  <hr />

  <h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>Our Site is not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us immediately.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>11. Third-Party Links</h2>
  <p>Our Site contains links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to review their privacy policies.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>12. Security</h2>
  <p>We implement reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>13. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post the updated policy on this page with a revised "Last updated" date. Continued use of the Site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new policy.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>14. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:</p>
  <p><strong>AI Tools Idea</strong><br />Email: privacy@aitoolsidea.com<br />Website: https://aitoolsidea.com</p>

</LegalLayout>
